sentences: Dalibor Davidović (born 3 January 1972 in Našice) is a musicologist and university professor.
He is currently researching the work of German artist Hans-Jürgen Syberberg.
From 2016 to 2018 visiting researcher at Berlin University of the Arts.
Istraživanja recepcije u muzikologiji i njihovi izgledi (Reception Research in Musicology and its Prospects), Zagreb: Croatian Musicological Society, 2002, ISBN 953-6090-19-8
